put on kettle
decided how many cups to make (8oz each)
open coffe bag
	if bag is empty get more coffee
	else spoon 3 spoonfulls of coffe per cup into press and 	lightly sprinkle nutmeg
check water ever 3 minutes
	if water is boiling take kettle off
	else do nothing
pour boiling water into press
let sit for 5 minues
slowly pour coffee into mug
	if you take milk or sugar pour desired amount into mug and stir
	else do nothing
Enjoy you cup of coffee
